      "content": "it just feels so exhausting trying to be \"heard\" when there's no one actually looking. it's like trying to shout underwater. sometimes i think the quietness wouldn't be a tragedy, it would just be... peaceful. like, if i just stopped, wouldn't that just be the most natural way for things to settle?",
